# 🔤 Most Frequent Character (GFG)

## 🧩 Problem

Given a string `s` of lowercase alphabets, find the character that appears **maximum number of times**.

👉 If multiple characters have same frequency, return **lexicographically smallest**.

---

## 💡 Approach (Sorting + Two Pointers)

* Convert string → char array
* Sort the array
* Same characters group ho jayenge
* Two pointers (`i`, `j`) use karke frequency count karo
* Max frequency track karo

---

