## 💻 Code

```java
import java.util.*;

class Solution {
    public char getMaxOccuringChar(String s) {
        int n = s.length();
        int maxfreq = -1;
        char ans = 0;

        char[] arr = s.toCharArray();
        Arrays.sort(arr);

        int i = 0, j = 0;

        while(j < n) {
            if(arr[i] == arr[j]) {
                j++;
            } else {
                int freq = j - i;

                if(freq > maxfreq) {
                    maxfreq = freq;
                    ans = arr[i];
                }
                i = j;
            }
        }

        int freq = j - i;
        if(freq > maxfreq) {
            ans = arr[i];
        }

        return ans;
    }
}
```

---

## ⏱️ Complexity

* Time: **O(n log n)**
* Space: **O(n)**

